    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You strike a creature up to one size category larger than yourself with a simple lariat, making an unarmed attack that deals damage as though you were one size category larger, and deals 2 additional damage per Strength Rank you are currently benefiting from (maximum +6 damage).<br><br>This technique may be used as part of a charge.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to make a trip attempt as a free action after the attack, without provoking an attack of opportunity.</p>\n",
